name: KNN Water Fertilty
description: 'KNN Water Fertility' is a K-Nearest Neighbors (KNN) analysis method that utilizes chlorophyll-a and phosphate parameters to assess the cleanliness and nutrient richness in a water source by identifying patterns and characteristics of its nearest neighbors.
